n                    </div>\n                  </div-->\n\n                  <div class=\"p-layer p-layer--03\">\n                    <div class=\"p-layer__inner\">\n                      <img class=\"p-layer__item\" src=\"/assets/images/top/hero_02_layer_03_color.png\">\n                      <img class=\"p-layer__item is-layer-gray\" src=\"/assets/images/top/hero_02_layer_03_gray.png\">\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n\n          <!-- NOTE: PC:スライド3枚目 //////////////////////////////////////// -->\n          <div class=\"p-hero-pc__item p-hero-pc__item--03\">\n            <div class=\"p-hero-pc__frame\">\n              <div class=\"p-hero-pc__inner\">\n                <div class=\"p-hero-pc__area\">\n\n                  <img class=\"p-hero-pc__mark\" src=\"/assets/images/top/hero_mark.png\">\n\n                  <div class=\"p-layer p-layer--01\">\n                    <div class=\"p-layer__inner\">\n                      <img class=\"p-layer__item\" src=\"/assets/images/top/hero_03_layer_01_color.png\">\n                      <img class=\"p-layer__item is-layer-gray\" src=\"/assets/images/top/hero_03_layer_01_gray.png\">\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div class=\"p-layer p-layer--02\">\n                    <div class=\"p-layer__inner\">\n                      <img class=\"p-layer__item\" src=\"/assets/images/top/hero_03_layer_02_color.png\">\n                      <img class=\"p-layer__item is-layer-gray\" src=\"/assets/images/top/hero_03_layer_02_gray.png\">\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div class=\"p-layer p-layer--03\">\n                    <div class=\"p-layer__inner\">\n                      <img class=\"p-layer__item\" src=\"/assets/images/top/hero_03_layer_03_color.png\">\n                      <img class=\"p-layer__item is-layer-gray\" src=\"/assets/images/top/hero_03_layer_03_gray.png\">\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div><!-- /.p-hero-pc -->\n      </div><!-- /.p-hero -->\n\n      \n      <div class=\"p-top-topic\">\n        \n        <a class=\"p-top-topic__link\" href=\"http://www.miyazaki-group.com/news/2025/04/446/\">\n        \n          <span class=\"p-top-topic__date\">2025/04/15</span>\n          <span class=\"p-top-topic__ttl\">宮崎商店がIBCラジオとコラボ&#x203c;</span>\n        </a>\n        \n        <p class=\"p-top-topic__btn\">\n          <a href=\"#anc-news-01\">\n            <img src=\"/assets/images/top/topic_icon_01_pc.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"sp-hidden\">\n          </a>\n        </p>\n      </div>\n      \n\n      <div class=\"l-contents u-pt-0\">\n\n        <section class=\"p-top-recruiting\">\n          <div class=\"p-top-recruiting__intro\">\n            <div class=\"c-inner c-inner--top\">\n              <div class=\"c-pict-unit\">\n                <p class=\"c-pict-unit__icon\">\n                  <img src=\"/assets/images/common/icon_page_recruiting.png\" alt=\"\">\n                </p>\n                <h2 class=\"c-pict-unit__hdg\">RECRUITING</h2>\n                <p class=\"c-pict-unit__txt\">仕事に夢中になっていると、時間が一瞬で過ぎていく。<br class=\"sp-hidden\">\n                  「ご苦労さん！」と言われて、見上げた空が夕焼けだったり。<br class=\"sp-hidden\">\n                  私たちをつき動かすもの、それはアツいハート。<br class=\"sp-hidden\">\n                  理屈ではない、目の前のことに一生懸命になるだけ。<br class=\"sp-hidden\">\n                  そのひたむきさが、その煌めきが、周りの人を笑顔にするなら、感動を産むなら<br class=\"sp-hidden\">\n                  それはとても嬉しいことだ。<br class=\"sp-hidden\">\n                  原動力は ...まっしぐらエンジン!\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"p-top-imgnav\">\n            <ul class=\"p-top-imgnav__list\">\n              <li class=\"p-top-imgnav__item c-parallax slide-bottom\">\n                <a class=\"p-top-imgnav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/01.html\">\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__img\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/top/recruiting_img_01.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__icon\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/top/recruiting_icon_01.png\" alt=\"MIYAZAKI RISING STARS! &#x23;001\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__name\">\n                    磯島　実<span>Minoru Isojima</span>\n                  </p>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"p-top-imgnav__item c-parallax slide-bottom\">\n                <a class=\"p-top-imgnav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/02.html\">\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__img\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/top/recruiting_img_02.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__icon\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/top/recruiting_icon_02.png\" alt=\"MIYAZAKI RISING STARS! &#x23;002\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__name\">\n                    三浦　圧次<span>Atsushi Miura</span>\n                  </p>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"p-top-imgnav__item c-parallax slide-bottom\">\n                <a class=\"p-top-imgnav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/03.html\">\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__img\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/top/recruiting_img_03.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__icon\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/top/recruiting_icon_03.png\" alt=\"MIYAZAKI RISING STARS! &#x23;003\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__name\">\n                    樋口　智一<span>Tomokazu Higuchi</span>\n                  </p>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"p-top-imgnav__item c-parallax slide-bottom\">\n                <a class=\"p-top-imgnav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/04.html\">\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__img\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/top/recruiting_img_04.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__icon\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/top/recruiting_icon_04.png\" alt=\"MIYAZAKI RISING STARS! &#x23;004\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__name\">\n                    荒澤　雄大<span>Yudai Arasawa</span>\n                  </p>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"p-top-imgnav__item c-parallax slide-bottom\">\n                <a class=\"p-top-imgnav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/05.html\">\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__img\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/top/recruiting_img_05.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__icon\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/top/recruiting_icon_05.png\" alt=\"MIYAZAKI RISING STARS! &#x23;005\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__name\">\n                    長谷川　牧子<span>Makiko Hasegawa</span>\n                  </p>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <!--li class=\"p-top-imgnav__item c-parallax slide-bottom\">\n                <a class=\"p-top-imgnav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/06.html\">\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__img\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/top/recruiting_img_06.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__icon\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/top/recruiting_icon_06.png\" alt=\"MIYAZAKI RISING STARS! &#x23;006\">\n                  </p>\n                  <p class=\"p-top-imgnav__name\">\n                    長谷川　牧子<span>Makiko Hasegawa</span>\n                  </p>\n                </a>\n              </li-->\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"p-top-business p-top-business--01 p-top-business--btn\">\n          <a class=\"p-top-business__link\" href=\"/business/car-life/\">\n            <div class=\"c-inner c-inner--top\">\n              <p class=\"p-top-business__icon\">\n                <img src=\"/assets/images/top/business_icon_car-life.png\" alt=\"\">\n              </p>\n              <h2 class=\"p-top-business__hdg\">CAR LIFE<span class=\"p-top-business__sub\">カーライフ事業</span></h2>\n              <p class=\"p-top-business__txt\">生活の必需品であり、毎日を楽しく豊かにしてくれる車。私たちはより安全、より快適なカーライフを実現するため、各種燃料の供給をはじめ、整備、タイヤなど走行パーツの販売取り付け、さらにボディケア等まで、カーライフを総合的にサポートしています。また、サービスステーステーションのコンサルアドバイザー部門をもち、内外SSのサ−ビス向上にも積極的に取り組んでいます。\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </a>\n          <!-- NOTE: ボタンがある場合は p-top-business に p-top-business--btn を付ける -->\n          <div class=\"p-top-business__nav\">\n            <ul class=\"p-top-business__nav__list\">\n              <li class=\"p-top-business__nav__item\">\n                <a class=\"p-top-business__nav__link\" href=\"https://xn--4it630auvkjkx.com/\">\n                  <span class=\"p-top-business__nav__txt\">\n                    <span class=\"p-top-business__nav__topics\">TOPICS!</span>特典満載！車検の情報はこちら\n                  </span>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n\n        <section class=\"p-top-business p-top-business--02\">\n          <a class=\"p-top-business__link\" href=\"/business/future-energy/\">\n            <div class=\"c-inner c-inner--top\">\n              <p class=\"p-top-business__icon\">\n                <img src=\"/assets/images/top/business_icon_mirai-energy.png\" alt=\"\">\n              </p>\n              <h2 class=\"p-top-business__hdg\">HOME ENERGY<span class=\"p-top-business__sub\">ホームエネルギー事業</span></h2>\n              <p class=\"p-top-business__txt\">毎日の暮らしに欠かせない、様々なエネルギーと設備の供給を担い皆様に快適さをご提供します。また、未来を見据えた次世代のエネルギーについての研究・開発も行っています。\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </a>\n          <!-- NOTE: ボタンがある場合は p-top-business に p-top-business--btn を付ける -->\n          <!-- <div class=\"p-top-business__nav\">\n            <ul class=\"p-top-business__nav__list\">\n              <li class=\"p-top-business__nav__item\">\n                <a class=\"p-top-business__nav__link\" href=\"/business/future-energy/lpg.html\">\n                  <span class=\"p-top-business__nav__txt\">\n                    <span class=\"p-top-business__nav__topics\">TOPICS!</span>LPGの価格表はこちら\n                  </span>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div> -->\n        </section>\n\n\n        <section class=\"p-top-business p-top-business--03\">\n          <a class=\"p-top-business__link\" href=\"/business/#anc-03\">\n            <div class=\"c-inner c-inner--top\">\n              <p class=\"p-top-business__icon\">\n                <img src=\"/assets/images/top/business_icon_entertainment.png\" alt=\"\">\n              </p>\n              <h2 class=\"p-top-business__hdg\">ENTERTAINMENT<span class=\"p-top-business__sub\">エンターテイメント事業</span></h2>\n              <p class=\"p-top-business__txt\">皆様の暮らしに潤いをお届けするとともに、地域のコミュニティスペースとして役立てていただき、より明るく健やかな社会に寄与。また、次世代の娯楽・リラクゼーション施設の開発も行っています。\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </a>\n        </section>\n\n\n        <div class=\"p-top-exterior\">\n          <ul class=\"p-top-exterior__list\">\n            <li class=\"p-top-exterior__item\">\n              <img src=\"/assets/images/top/exterior_img_01.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"p-top-exterior__item\">\n              <img src=\"/assets/images/top/exterior_img_02.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"p-top-exterior__item\">\n              <img src=\"/assets/images/top/exterior_img_03.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"p-top-exterior__item\">\n    